                dates="May 2022 – Present"
                description="Product manager driving AI-powered tools and data automation. Expert in translating complex business logic into intuitive user solutions, delivering high-impact features with speed and precision."
                bullets={[
                    "Trusted product leader and subject-matter expert, partnering closely with engineering to create user tools and optimize core business logic.",
